---
// Testimonials section component
---

<section id="testimonials" class="testimonials">
  <div class="testimonials-container">
    <h2 class="section-title">What Clients Say</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Trusted by industry leaders and innovative companies worldwide
    </p>
    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-header">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar">
            <img src="/tusharkulkarni.jpeg" alt="Tushar Kulkarni" />
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-info">
            <h4>Tushar Kulkarni</h4>
            <span>CEO, Big Kitty Labs</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-quote">
          <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
          <p>He is very resourceful and fast. His ability to deliver high-quality solutions quickly has been instrumental to our success. Damilola consistently exceeds expectations with his technical expertise.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rating">
          <span>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-header">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar">
            <img src="/ericwagner.jpeg" alt="Eric Wagner" />
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-info">
            <h4>Eric Wagner</h4>
            <span>CEO, Ubihere</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-quote">
          <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
          <p>We would like to have people like you on our team physically. His technical expertise and work ethic are exceptional. Damilola brings both skill and professionalism to every project.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rating">
          <span>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-header">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar">
            <div class="avatar-placeholder">CL</div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-info">
            <h4>Chris Lundgren</h4>
            <span>Credit Glory</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-quote">
          <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
          <p>His speed almost seems unreal. The quality and efficiency of his work consistently exceeds our expectations. Damilola delivers results that drive real business impact.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rating">
          <span>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: #000000;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .testimonials::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 70% 80%, rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .testimonials-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #f1f5f9;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: #0f172a;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .testimonial-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #60a5fa, #3b82f6);
  }

  .testimonial-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.03) 0%, transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .testimonial-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .testimonial-card:hover::after {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .testimonial-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-avatar {
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 3px solid #60a5fa;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .testimonial-avatar img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .avatar-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #60a5fa, #3b82f6);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .testimonial-info h4 {
    color: #f1f5f9;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .testimonial-info span {
    color: #60a5fa;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .testimonial-quote {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .quote-icon {
    position: absolute;
    top: -15px;
    left: -10px;
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: #60a5fa;
    opacity: 0.2;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .testimonial-quote p {
    color: #e5e7eb;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .rating {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .rating span {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3));
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .testimonial-card {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .testimonial-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .testimonial-avatar {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
    }

    .testimonial-quote p {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .quote-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
      top: -12px;
      left: -8px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>